{{Top|leg}}
A '''suppressor tube''' was a type of device which would disable [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. If a [[Human/Legends|Human]] or other organic being stood too close to the object being suppressed, the tool would also affect the being, though the exact effects were unknown.

[[Olag Greck]], under the code name Mollo, suppressed [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]], mistaking him for his droid [[C-3PX]], an [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassination droid]] whom Olag wanted to appear at his droid fighting venue on [[Hosk Station/Legends|Hosk Station]].

{{Tech-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The suppressor tube shares the same purpose as an [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannon]], although to a lesser extent. Whether the suppressor tube is a limited-production tool, a custom creation by Olag Greck, or a variation of an ion cannon is unknown.

